<section id="itsm_locQualityIssueType">
    <title>locQualityIssueType</title>
    
    <para>Localization Quality Issue Type - the <code>locQualityIssueType</code> attribute is the
            <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink> defined
            <code>locQualityIssueType</code> attribute.</para>
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> a text string, exactly one value from the
        following list:</para>
    <para> <simplelist>
    
        <member><code>terminology</code></member>
        <member><code>mistranslation</code></member>
        <member><code>omission</code></member>
        <member><code>untranslated</code></member>
        <member><code>addition</code></member>
        <member><code>duplication</code></member>
        <member><code>inconsistency</code></member>
        <member><code>grammar</code></member>
        <member><code>legal</code></member>
        <member><code>register</code></member>
        <member><code>locale-specific-content</code></member>
        <member><code>locale-violation</code></member>
        <member><code>style</code></member>
        <member><code>characters</code></member>
        <member><code>misspelling</code></member>
        <member><code>typographical</code></member>
        <member><code>formatting</code></member>
        <member><code>inconsistent-entities</code></member>
        <member><code>numbers</code></member>
        <member><code>markup</code></member>
        <member><code>pattern-problem</code></member>
        <member><code>whitespace</code></member>
        <member><code>internationalization</code></member>
        <member><code>length</code></member>
        <member><code>non-conformance</code></member>
        <member><code>uncategorized</code></member>
        <member><code>other</code></member>
        
        
        
        
    </simplelist></para>
    <para>For normative usage description and informative guidance for the above values, see <olink
            targetdoc="../../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink>
        <ulink url="http://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#lqissue-typevalues"
            >http://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#lqissue-typevalues</ulink>.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis>: undefined</para>
    
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk"
            ><code>&lt;mrk></code></olink> and
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sm.xml"
            targetptr="sm"><code>&lt;sm></code></olink>, or in <olink targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssue.xml"
                targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssue"><code>&lt;locQualityIssue></code></olink>.</para>
    
    
    <para>See the <olink targetdoc="../../modules/itsm/Localization_Quality_Issue.xml" targetptr="lqiAnnotation"
            >ITS Localization Issue Annotation</olink> for the normative usage description of this
        attribute when used inline; advanced Constraints follow from that normative usage
        description.</para>
    <para>See <olink targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssue.xml"
            targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssue"><code>&lt;locQualityIssue></code></olink> for standoff
        usage Constraints.</para>
    
</section>
